reviewText: So excited it came in early. The quality is very good.
My grandkids took it home now I got to get another one.  They liked it so much
Fascinating scenes and easy for a child to follow. Grown ups loved to watch it too! Wish there are more.
I recently saw this movie on Encore and became an instant fan. I enjoyed the twist of the classic story of Cinderella infused with the Old West. Ingenious.
We love this movie so excited we found it. Fast shipping and cheap.  She watches this movie more than the disney version
I enjoy watching by myself without the kids.  It is a cute retelling of Cinderella and entertaining without being silly like most children's story these days
